{"word":"συνεπαίρω","slug":"συνεπαίρω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συνεπαίρω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ᾰρῶ</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to raise</i> or <i>lift at the same time</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be elevated together with</i>, <el>τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to urge on together</i> or <i>also</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to rise together with</i> others, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}